Title: They fury
DateModified: '2019-03-10'
DatePublished: '2019-03-10'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/they-fury
SetInCountry: Egypt
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Ana Florencia Carotti
AuthorCountry: Argentina
Text: 'Arab Spring. News of freedom. Tears. Chaos. A revolution from inside. What
  is happening? Why are the Americans leaving in convoys? What will happen to us?


  Reality seen, not form the perspective of locals who naturalize outbursts or far
  away journalists who speak of the light at the end of the tunnel, but from a third
  world country family navigating da gerois waters with no crew or direction.'
